{"tid":1497093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於今晚823人鏈我有一點擔心","createTime":"2019-08-22T21:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T03:09:21.000Z","uid":294955,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5185fa653cfa56f597e41dacb62e03ce0d966ffd","tid":1497093,"uid":294955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T21:15:42.000Z","msg":"今晚可能發生嘅事:<br />\n1. 企一個鐘，足以畀人扮攝記影參與者大頭相，去做個龐大和理非抗爭者資料庫<br />\n<br />\n2. 鄉黑，大陸白衣人，藍絲趁機多區進行聯合傷人行動，尤其在較偏僻陰暗的地點和紅區，警方不執法<br />\n<br />\n3. 有批黑警鬼扮參與者，過程中與路人爭執，其後警方出現直接以非法集結集會等理由拘捕其他參與者（主辦單位FB已提及）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">萬一明晚壯舉因人少唔成事，記得塞翁先馬嘅道理。</span>"},{"pid":"57d6b8890eb49b771a878b89241649d9c99b7455","tid":1497093,"uid":248925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:02:50.000Z","msg":"呢個真 即使個活動幾和平都好 啲狗係要搞你就搞你<br />\n發夢都起碼有條防線同人群集中做保護，依家全部人打散三區仲要淨企，真係幾撚危<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不過去左先，越多人越安全</strong></span>"},{"pid":"61d195bb701676db1b74d29e9cdc95ca281236d9","tid":1497093,"uid":290355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:11:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定要小心有人一條掃晒所有抗爭者樣入資料庫,必需做好遮樣準備!</span>"},{"pid":"eab407440f27deba7bd9ae935562f6b3e60457a5","tid":1497093,"uid":290355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:14:05.000Z","msg":"大家要小心呀"},{"pid":"72330d9aff1041e1781c6f1de10230fdbe109304","tid":1497093,"uid":294955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:26:27.000Z","msg":"今日8.23東方頭版大字廣告<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">似係向藍絲發暗號做嘢</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/agqypQS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FagqypQS.png&h=38388bfa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8cf9d5f8913eb710ef3543f8bc2c32701cbb5cd","tid":1497093,"uid":290355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:09:21.000Z","msg":"<i